{"tid":1243151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［民意戰］係衝之前，不如搞大呢幾單野保留民意先","createTime":"2019-06-19T10:36:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T14:25:54.000Z","uid":117251,"like":66,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"2723ac1f9bd0fdfb2047392bc53e4cb04f1aa041","tid":1243151,"uid":117251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:36:42.000Z","msg":"我發夢夢到621可能好多人都認為要包圍甚至衝擊<br />\n無錯，deadline 過左，勇武朋友係有需要進一步行動<br />\n但我地要衝得有原因<br />\n民意係衝擊最好既理由，亦都係一道保護<br />\n<br />\n612當日點解會發夢發得咁好咁有迴響？<br />\n係要先有69百萬人遊行而被林鄭一野say no<br />\n依家我地拎左二百萬人支持<br />\n就要好好keep住，唔好俾呢兩日政府既「假讓步」扯走<br />\n<br />\n所以除左文宣要不停提醒呢班人<br />\n我地要繼續搞大啲新聞<br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1.醫管局- 病人資料被警犬後門得到</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://doctordaddysoccer.blogspot.com/2019/06/MIIDSS.html?fbclid=IwAR3-jLATbGVXpS-iYHEzHElgy30ZfIOv8QVTK7bfSn30VzM39zVH0qCE4AA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdoctordaddysoccer.blogspot.com%2F2019%2F06%2FMIIDSS.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3-jLATbGVXpS-iYHEzHElgy30ZfIOv8QVTK7bfSn30VzM39zVH0qCE4AA&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyu4eNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=82e97456\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://doctordaddysoccer.blogspot.com/2019/06/MIIDSS.html?fbclid=IwAR3-jLATbGVXpS-iYHEzHElgy30ZfIOv8QVTK7bfSn30VzM39zVH0qCE4AA</a><br />\n<br />\n呢單野記者會之後就無曬聲氣<br />\n無人繼續追究佢<br />\n講梗唔只今次被捕人士，係一直以來黎求醫既病人既資料都外洩，甚至警方係隨時可以透過紀錄監控你既一舉一動<br />\n係同<span style=\"color: red;\">市民莫大關係</span>，議員好應該繼續追擊，同話俾市民知件事有幾嚴重<br />\n有好多人其實仲以為警犬拎資料去醫院拉人無問題<br />\n要煲大佢，俾全世界知個問題嚴重性<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2.中信大廈事件 -警犬對有不反對通知書既合法集會施放催淚彈</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1242409/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1242409/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n 呢件最近有片睇到當時狀況，但係聲氣唔夠<br />\n既然當時民陣係申請左合法<br />\n呢單就絕對大條道理去追討<br />\n但又係無乜議員提，又無記者問<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3.警察濫用武力</span></span><br />\n呢樣大把例證，唔止一條片警察用過份武力打學生，打記者<br />\n再加上無警員編號，投訴無門，監警會又無調查權同懲處權，基本上警察權力大到就算有失當失職都耐佢唔何<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1242366/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1242366/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1242232/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1242232/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190619/59734297?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1DgsUFeHv4quzOVbCvU3xp7Ndb3rUkfSC13QPsGyXapVVfTYsJIjmy00A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190619%2F59734297%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1DgsUFeHv4quzOVbCvU3xp7Ndb3rUkfSC13QPsGyXapVVfTYsJIjmy00A&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyu4eNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=2684c038\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190619%2F59734297%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1DgsUFeHv4quzOVbCvU3xp7Ndb3rUkfSC13QPsGyXapVVfTYsJIjmy00A&h=b1fcebb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190619/59734297?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1DgsUFeHv4quzOVbCvU3xp7Ndb3rUkfSC13QPsGyXapVVfTYsJIjmy00A</a><br />\n今日立法會已經有質詢，但未夠，條撚屌李家超乜都答唔出，最好捉埋盧偉聰一齊對質<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢啲都係近排政府既醜聞，呢啲都要議員，記者，文宣大大力咁炒起<br />\n最好每日一大單<br />\n要保留甚至增加民意，令大眾繼續對政府失去信心<br />\n咁我地就算圍就算衝都好都有好大既民意推動<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"ba690b39cef5a144ce6ff81b4ea8a0e4ef5e110f","tid":1243151,"uid":241363,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:37:39.000Z","msg":"3單都好應該煲大佢"},{"pid":"2cec0099d45c99eedb3a5428f9cfb6880e3392da","tid":1243151,"uid":94167,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:38:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b604aa989627c3721d59e3987c0a14ea5e0f3b64","tid":1243151,"uid":1080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:39:19.000Z","msg":"推 呢幾單一定搞大佢"},{"pid":"533305062cebc48c95710b33be21ff0ff32f6f5d","tid":1243151,"uid":69746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:40:07.000Z","msg":"推 搞撚大佢"},{"pid":"30e558afd67f835457c0ca0b812882e6914b1579","tid":1243151,"uid":33733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:41:01.000Z","msg":"推 警權過大非常危險"},{"pid":"cd7c283422985e948a9efed5ff448a9dc24193d1","tid":1243151,"uid":38568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:41:19.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"d877fa015b25550c384989d0b363f9ec802c9574","tid":1243151,"uid":93932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:41:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"255bd2aeb198cd4ac7d0b08dea0a5d75e0ad80d1","tid":1243151,"uid":156936,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:44:07.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n雖然呢個post唔關禮賓府係關立法會事，不過都阻阻大家宣傳一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n夢見好多人想開放日遊覽禮賓府。<br />\n但聽聞條斜路好危險，驚人多出現意外。<br />\n為安全著想，出席任何活動前，<span style=\"color: red;\">大家都有義務了解該地環境</span>，<br />\n希望各位唔好一知半解的情況下跟隨人流，造成危險。<br />\n===============<br />\n建議巴士路線及巴士站<br />\n===============<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pZoOuRy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpZoOuRy.jpg&h=6ca9e50d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5v6z9Rz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5v6z9Rz.jpg&h=7291e991&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n===============<br />\n建議地鐵步行路線<br />\n===============<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JUqEBwz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJUqEBwz.jpg&h=f978913f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n===============================<br />\n禮賓府高空、地則及2018香港地圖懶人包<br />\n===============================<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YFueqpV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYFueqpV.jpg&h=2680d5df&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n===============<br />\n<br />\n樓主現時收集以下的資料及圖片，作學術研究之用 :<br />\n1. 禮賓府正確的出入口和閘門總數<br />\n2. 禮賓府旁舊樓梯及非行車小徑等Google Map無法標示之通道<br />\n3. 急救站、飲水機、洗手間或可設立急救站空地等休息位置<br />\n4. 野生犬隻出沒或聚居地點 (可以Google map mark比我最好)<br />\n5. 由蘭桂坊或香港動植物公園前往的最佳路線<br />\n<br />\n歡迎加入討論: <strong>圖解香港禮賓府旅遊路線</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1241712/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1241712/page/1</a><br />\n更多細節請用追故模式"},{"pid":"0de0be0f8bda6169402cbb86d0c9a7719461abbf","tid":1243151,"uid":87326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:45:07.000Z","msg":"對升級有幫助既就推"},{"pid":"5b81fe7cc7c47bb70513cfab6ce0caaf95e90ad1","tid":1243151,"uid":32149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:45:28.000Z","msg":"呢幾單直頭可以做嚟緊衝嘅理由啦<br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，阻一阻大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家廣傳整合post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[同我推晒佢] 力抗膠post 621行動討論整合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1242813\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1242813</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"aff194dc4c99238f52fd23c48ab3603b2acb7dff","tid":1243151,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:45:41.000Z","msg":"喺各大社交平台散開去"},{"pid":"da82b119b99bb954bdee6436d1c99f9eac1a7c92","tid":1243151,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:47:13.000Z","msg":"繼續首推撤回已經聚唔到咁多民氣，依家好應該轉換焦點"},{"pid":"aa008928c458d4b4a29cc616a295abb1ca181b63","tid":1243151,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:47:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mRvECQR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmRvECQR.png&h=111d4d1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/84QECQX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F84QECQX.png&h=e1cac3d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oFW06Kp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoFW06Kp.png&h=1af1cfc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你或者身邊既人仲諗緊620、621好唔好出黎...請入一入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1243130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1243130</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3f473a0219fd737c694bbc7a1c19bb8925c390cf","tid":1243151,"uid":117251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:48:04.000Z","msg":"另外，<br />\n仲有份道歉聲明<br />\n除左示威者對市民<br />\n仲可以加幾句係學生對家長<br />\n道歉聲明係剛<br />\n子女父母關係係柔，要動之以情<br />\n<br />\n可以寫話<br />\n始終衝突會出現危險，<br />\n明白父母好擔心子女既生命安危同前途<br />\n<br />\n之後就話但係為世所迫<br />\n如果唔企出黎<br />\n就可能唔洗旨意講前途"},{"pid":"22bea2bc7cd64c3243da60fffe3f8a9bf52ab5fb","tid":1243151,"uid":50762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:48:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8nNvKxq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8nNvKxq.png&h=c6a7c060&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZoaX8Y5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZoaX8Y5.png&h=edeed655&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"32bf9f0b0d116d3d5c9c55041db7f8d502ec9c71","tid":1243151,"uid":117251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:48:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ebf52711363900dcd6186aea85aeee4401923795","tid":1243151,"uid":172627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:48:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5b9f9df6ae4a5df4368bb6cdc8aac039df77adc","tid":1243151,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:49:09.000Z","msg":"Agree"},{"pid":"9146f7a05929adc01362fe559775924d9a37abb1","tid":1243151,"uid":117251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:53:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1dd5b0e6b3078f8b5afd579e3f3346c908c4fb68","tid":1243151,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:54:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f9a0851a4065f87cbc883f672e3c58e01a77cca3","tid":1243151,"uid":117251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:34:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8490ef11ed95871b34f9f7203489553e65e95722","tid":1243151,"uid":243834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:39:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"50e74141efdf6f93efc7c33eaab8b1c118df04b5","tid":1243151,"uid":117251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:59:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"966c6ddaf21ca396b1ba82d73aa19c3d3e259924","tid":1243151,"uid":43022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:01:26.000Z","msg":"pish"}]}